      "span_text": "Instead, we would like to make a Markov assumption over the edges of the tree, in a similar way that a Markov assumption can be made for sequential classification problems in order to ensure tractable learning and inference. [CITATION_1] distinguish between two kinds of Markovization for unlexicalized CFG parsing."
